## <a id="1803.10"></a>1803.10

**Release Date**: May 22, 2019

### Features
- Platform Engineers can deploy Windows Stemcells on a BOSH Director with Google Cloud Storage as their external Blobstore. 
- Improved Troubleshooting of Windows VMs, with ssh enabled by default for all Windows VMs. You can still disable SSH in the PASW tile.
- Includes Microsoft Security Updates to protect against Microarchitectural Data Sampling side-channel vulnerabilities. For more information, see [May 14, 2019—KB4499167 (OS Build 17134.765)](https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4494441/windows-10-update-kb4494441) in the Windows support documentation.

